{{Quote|You ever wonder what makes Rodians look all puckered all the time? It's that ''poodoo'' they call "ale" -- they drink it all the time and it just makes their faces get all twisty, like somebody painted them and tried to make 'em look even funnier than they already did.|[[Ezil|Old Ezil]]|<ref name="Ezil's Return">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/livingforce/swlf20041118b|text=Ezil's Return}}</ref>}}
